      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, always garaged, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
