    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a pristine 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a wide-body icon featuring the M96/03 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus variable valve timing. This example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a flawless G96/00 six-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical symbiosis of the viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system and the factory-spec M030 sport suspension provide unparalleled turn-in precision and high-speed stability. The braking system remains sharp, utilizing four-piston monoblock calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors. Every component, from the intake manifold to the rear limited-slip differential, has been maintained to exacting standards, ensuring this vehicle performs with the same visceral feedback as it did on day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
